  "description": "# Season 8: Intent Ratification\n\nIntents are high level strategic goals the entire Collective works towards. All contributions in the Collective should be working towards the Intents.\n\nIn Season 8, we will have one [Intent](https://gov.optimism.io/t/season-8-intent/10009), focused on a core pillar of our Superchain Product Vision: **Interoperability**. This is consistent with our Season 7 Intent, as the Collective remains focused on delivering protocol-native interop and preparing the ecosystem for successful adoption.\n\nIntent: A set of **interoperable** Stage 1 chains doing $100m per month in cross-chain asset transfers\n\nRatification implies support of this strategic goal as the main focus for the Collective during Season 8.\n\nThis proposal is eligible for Special Voting Cycle #39a: <https://gov.optimism.io/t/special-voting-cycle-roundup-39a/10064>\n\nThe proposal is subject to Joint House ratification, as outlined in the [Operating Manual](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/OPerating-manual/blob/main/manual.md).",
